Eighteenth Ave., east side, from and including 81st to and including 82nd Streets, showing the Van Pelt Manor. Also showing between the two benches in the foreground, is the milestone which reads:- 8 1/4 miles to New York Ferry. This road to Denys' Ferry 2 1/2 miles; 10 1/2 miles to New York Ferry. This road to Jamaica 15 miies. It also marked the postroad from Boston to Philadelphia.
1922.
